Text: There needs to be more bands like this!
gr8 stuff!!! This band is fuckin awesome \m/..

Its not a band, its a project.
And there are, called Aina :) - just as great!
Aina is a progressive metal supergroup, containing members from all over the world and from all strands of metal and hard rock. Tobias Sammet is involved in this project also...
Great music but listen also to Gary Hughes - Once and a future king part I & II. Is also great.
